# Corpus artifacts are binary. Without this, core.autocrlf=true rewrites LF->CRLF
# on checkout (git classifies reportlab PDFs as "text" — they have no early NUL),
# corrupting the PDF xref on fresh clones (Vercel/CI). That silently disabled the
# live /extract Bedrock path. Marking them binary keeps bytes intact on checkout.
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
